episodes.title: Secret recording elders w df'd after 5th letter for reinstatement ep 19
episodes.description:
So this is after I submitted my 5th letter I turned it in, they spoke w me after I jumped through all their hoops from the previous 4 letters. They send this 5th letter to my df'fing congregation in Oconomowoc South, then Oconomowoc South set up a reinstatement meeting w me only to cancel it two hours before it was to happen, this recording will explain why Oconomowoc South cancelled but in the process two dorks get upset and  one elder who's nice remains pleasant.
They get upset because I resist them,  as they equate their inquiry to God. That's when I finally felt like I had my life in my own hands which is where every woman and man's individual life should be in their own hands. Never give up your power to oppressors misusing the scriptures ESPECIALLY when God has neither confirmed or denied their supposed authority over you.
